们告诉他，一位武汉的 S 先生，张继科欠他很多的钱，于是 S 先生向张讨债。在此前后，张继科给了几段明星某女士的隐私视频给 S 先生。S 先生转而向某女士要钱，结果某女士报案，S 先生在 2020 年 2 月被抓。张继科借贷合同被曝光：借款利率是银行商贷的 4 倍"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f3ffdecfd701429d17e53c6322c65b32_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "240 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593439613"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIt5Ghv4Hj4JVKEAMaCDk0MTU3MTQ4ILG8qKEGMDc47wlABXIJNTkzNDM5NjEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1680527495.5018582", "card_id": "Q_593352240", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "意大利或将立法禁止官方交流中使用英语，违者最高罚款 10 万欧元，原因有哪些？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，意大利执政党——意大利兄弟党向众议院提议，设立法律禁止使用外语，违反者最高罚款 10 万欧元（约合 74.4 万元人民币）。目前，这一立法提议已经得到了意大利总理梅洛尼的支持。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-28a058d45291313090125c97e0c60881_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "219 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593352240"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It5Ghv4Hj4JVKEAMaCDk0MTM3NjkzINv9pKEGMAc43QFABnIJNTkzMzUyMjQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1680527495.5027747", "card_id": "Q_593499925", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 Falcom 社长近藤季洋对谈米哈游制作人，称受到了《星穹铁道》「莫大的鼓励」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "游研社：Falcom 米哈游跨国对谈：回合制 RPG 将向何处？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9c8efd5812eef3e4b30ce4b51b96cb6b_1440w.jpg?source=172ae18b"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "161 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"ur